- The float RE is: `^[+-]?((\d*\.\d+)|(\d+\.\d*))$`
- The scientific notation RE is: `^[+-]?((\d*\.\d+)|(\d+(\.\d*)?))[eE][+-]?\d+$`

We can combine them as one: `^[+-]?((\d*\.\d+)|(\d+(\.\d*)?))([eE][+-]?\d+)?$`

    class Solution(object):
